data.description: You cannot miss out on the opportunity to view this amazing Tri-Level in Franklin.In the last five years, this beautiful home has been completely updated featuring vaulted ceilings, fireplace, new beautiful large picture windows allowing a bunch of natural lighting, new roof, all new kitchen with tiled backsplash, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, high end cabinetry and fixtures, new flooring throughout the entire home, new paint, lighting fixtures, electrical, plumbing, furnace, central air, water heater, New concrete patio, new driveway and front porch.Property is wired with high fi audio and hue lighting system.This amazing property sits on almost 1/2 acre of beautiful green grass and mature trees you will love the new home feel in a wonderfully seasoned home
